reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and well made coasters.
reviews.reviewText: I bought these coasters for my cubicle at work. They do a great job at keeping sweat from my cups off papers. The color has stayed true for the 1.5 months since I bought them. They are also very trendy and cute. Great value for the price, as they came with 6. I only use two in my office, and the rest are used at home. Very happy with my purchase, and will purchase other colors if I decide to change the “color theme” of my decor!

reviews.reviewText: I got a pack of six and handed them out to coworkers. They feel nice and add a cozy element to your desk. They're pretty thick and feel high quality. I like them.
